cscie97.asn2.housemate.model

Class House

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn2.housemate.model.House
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Occupant, Room

    public abstract class House
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that represents a house.The attributes are common to all houses and each entity we are modeling is unique such as Room or Occupant.
    See Also:
    HouseMateAPI, Occupant, Room
